metadata.name: Bally Gang #1
metadata.description: The Bally Gang NFT is a collection of 8,888 NFT'S with real life and virtual utilities. Launched on the Ethereum Blockchain with over 300 traits in 3D, each NFT is unique and exclusive. Bally Gang NFT holders are a part of an exclusive community full of like minded people with an interest in entertainment, business and nft enthusiasts who believe in the future of crypto-currencies and blockchain technology.
